        Mortgagee in Possession Sale in Queensland: What Sellers Facing Financial Hardship Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        When a lender exercises the power of sale, the borrower loses control of the process. Understanding what this means, and what you can still do, matters.
      </p>
